      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a budget-friendly fixer-upper? This vehicle is a diamond in the rough, ready for a dedicated new owner to bring it back to its former glory! While it currently requires some significant mechanical attention and cosmetic TLC, it's a fantastic opportunity for a handy DIYer or someone looking for a solid parts car. If you're ready to put in some elbow grease, this car is waiting for its second chance at the road!",
