    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-grade example of automotive excellence that defies its age. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, appearing today exactly as it did on the showroom floor. The exterior finish retains a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely no road rash, stone chips, or swirl marks, further enhanced by a professionally applied multi-stage ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in a 'time capsule' state; the premium leather upholstery is supple with zero bolster wear or creasing, and the carpets have been protected by original mats since new. Every switch, dial, and electronic feature operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history with every maintenance interval performed ahead of schedule by master technicians. This is a rare opportunity to own a flawless, collector-quality vehicle. Sale includes all original keys, the window sticker, complete service binders, and a custom-fit indoor car cover.",
      "price": 48500.0,
